reviewText: It was just ok, the story needed more development.
This movie was not what I expected, didn't like the ending, very low budget movie
i do not like the way the movie ended it did not make any sense no closure but the dvd was in good condition,thank you GOD BLESS U.

This movie was weird, if you going to have 2 sisters going after the same man, You should had him with someone, and this movie did not have a GOOD ending at all, I thought the way it was going, you was going to put the homeless man with the older Sister, and the younger Sister she was not ready for no relationship at all, I wish I could get a REFUND.
This movie was not what I expected it to be, I didn't like the way it ended. The Deacon didn't know the women were trying to get him to like him. The movie wasn't that good.

Deacon Wyles acted as if he did not know that those sisters liked him. Are you kidding? Are you that blind? This was a waste of money. I never do like when a woman chases a man. I think that it should be the other way around. If you have faith in God, you won't have to chase, she will be there when you least expect it. I believe. I would not of brought this dvd if I had seen the previews.
Contrary to some of the other reviews, this movie is worth it. The acting is not bad considering the actors are not well-known. The ending will leave you upset.
The movie started slow and on top of that the ending wasn't complete. It left off with you wondering don't buy it.
This is a very good movie.  Lots of laughter and the movie kept you interested.  A really good movie.  Love it.
